+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Geochronology/Division/QMIS004> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Marine Isotope Stage 4 (Late Pleistocene) (Geologic Time Scale 2020, fig. 30.2; BGS British Regional Geology: Northern England (Fifth edition), fig. 64)."@en .
